'''SIG MCX'''是一款由[[西格&紹爾|西格&紹爾]]所研製及生產的一系列[[卡賓槍|卡賓槍]]，採用了從[[SIG_MPX衝鋒槍|SIG MPX衝鋒槍]]結轉改進而成的[[氣動式_(槍械)#短行程活塞傳動|短行程導氣活塞氣動式]]系統，並且具有[[半自動步枪|半自動]]型和[[擊發調變槍械|擊發調變]]（[[突擊步枪|突擊步枪]]）型兩種配置。<ref name="Sig Sauer 2017 Catalog">{{cite web|title=2017 SIG SAUER Catalog|url=http://html5.dcatalog.com/?docid=f2593e6b-bc3c-408a-94f0-a6fe00f6b421#page=42|website=dcatalog.com|publisher=SIG Sauer|access-date=26 February 2017|archive-date=2018-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007040335/http://html5.dcatalog.com/?docid=f2593e6b-bc3c-408a-94f0-a6fe00f6b421#page=42|dead-url=no}}</ref>目前可發射[[5.56×45mm_NATO|5.56×45毫米]][[北大西洋公约组织|北约]]、{{Link-en|300 AAC Blackout (7.62×35mm)|300 AAC Blackout (7.62×35mm)|.300 AAC BLK（7.62×35毫米）}}和[[7.62×39mm|7.62×39毫米蘇聯]]（M43）這三種[[口徑|口徑]]的[[步枪|步枪]][[子彈|子彈]]。

於[[西格&紹爾|西格&紹爾]]在新罕布什爾州的工廠建製的SIG MCX，根據西格&紹爾小冊子對該步槍的描述，為“經過徹底改造以後成為短、輕量、消聲”的武器。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-florida-shooting-sigsauer-idUSKCN0Z12EA|publisher=Reuters|date=15 June 2016|title=Sig Sauer, maker of Orlando gunman's weapon, is expanding rapidly in U.S.|first=Tim|last=McLaughlin|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2016-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914203330/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-florida-shooting-sigsauer-idUSKCN0Z12EA|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2016年，SIG召回了一些使用第一代槍栓機框的該槍型。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sofrep.com/70713/sig-sauer-mcx-mandatory-recall/|title=Sig Sauer MCX Mandatory Recall|website=SOFREP News|date=24 December 2014|accessdate=2018-03-18|archive-date=2018-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180318183223/https://sofrep.com/70713/sig-sauer-mcx-mandatory-recall/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://sofrep.com/70713/sig-sauer-mcx-mandatory-recall/|title=Sig Sauer MCX Mandatory Recall|date=24 December 2014|website=SOFREP News|accessdate=2018-03-18|archive-date=2018-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180318183223/https://sofrep.com/70713/sig-sauer-mcx-mandatory-recall/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 設計細節 ==
SIG MCX系列了[[氣動式_(槍械)#短行程活塞傳動|短行程導氣活塞氣動式]]系統，以減少[[後座力|後座力]]，提高了武器的可靠性；這是基於先前推出的[[SIG_MPX衝鋒槍|SIG MPX]]的設計。<ref name=GA>{{cite web|title=First Look: SIG Sauer MCX|author=G&A Online Editors|date=January 13, 2015|publisher=Guns & Ammo|url=http://www.gunsandammo.com/first-look/sig-sauer-mcx/|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2016-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161020234135/http://www.gunsandammo.com/first-look/sig-sauer-mcx/|dead-url=no}}</ref>MCX具有一個可讓該卡賓槍在[[5.56×45mm_NATO|5.56×45毫米]][[北大西洋公约组织|北约]][[口徑|口徑]]、{{Link-en|300 AAC Blackout (7.62×35mm)|300 AAC Blackout (7.62×35mm)|.300 AAC BLK（7.62×35毫米）口徑}}、[[7.62×39mm|7.62×39毫米蘇聯口徑]]之間的轉換的系統，5.56×45毫米北约口徑和.300 AAC BLK（7.62×35毫米）口徑時使用標準的5.56×45毫米口徑的[[STANAG彈匣|STANAG彈匣]]，而7.62×39毫米蘇聯口徑則是特別設計的STANAG兼容彈匣。<ref name=GA/><ref name="TTAG">{{cite web|url=http://www.thetruthaboutguns.com/2015/10/foghorn/gun-review-sig-sauer-mcx/|title=Gun Review: SIG SAUER MCX|date=October 17, 2015|work=The Truth About Guns|accessdate=June 23, 2016|first=Nick|last=Leghorn|archive-date=2016-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008034848/http://www.thetruthaboutguns.com/2015/10/foghorn/gun-review-sig-sauer-mcx/|dead-url=no}}</ref>MCX的設計是用於提供發射.300 AAC BLK（7.62×35毫米）口徑步槍和可選用的[[抑制器|消聲器]]的最優性能。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.americanrifleman.org/articles/2015/1/20/sig-sauer-mcx-carbine/|title=SIG Sauer MCX Carbine|work=American Rifleman|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2016-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160911000124/https://www.americanrifleman.org/articles/2015/1/20/sig-sauer-mcx-carbine/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

槍管採用錐形槍口，此設計為抑制器部門主管Kevin Brittingham所引入，使得該槍可裝上[[槍口|槍口]]裝置和直接螺紋裝拆式[[抑制器|消聲器]]而無需擔心因不使用墊圈導致性能下降，而且可讓裝置裝上以後自行定於中間。槍管可以在短時間內改變為另一長度或不同的口徑。此外，槍管表面塗上了[[氮化物|氮化物]]塗層以提高耐腐蝕性。<ref name=Merrill2015>{{cite web|url=http://www.recoilweb.com/recoil-exclusive-breakdown-of-the-sig-mcx-56367.html|first=David|last=Merrill|publisher=Recoil|title=RECOIL Exclusive: Breakdown of the Sig MCX|year=2015|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2016-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161025031623/http://www.recoilweb.com/recoil-exclusive-breakdown-of-the-sig-mcx-56367.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=warden>{{cite web|title=Full Review: SIG Sauer MCX|first=Drew|last=Warden|date=October 7, 2015|url=http://www.gundigest.com/tactical-gear/full-review-sig-sauer-mcx|publisher=Gun Digest|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2016-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161030163717/http://www.gundigest.com/tactical-gear/full-review-sig-sauer-mcx|dead-url=no}}</ref>它具有淬火鋼磨損點。<ref name=GA/><ref name=Merrill2015/>

所有MCX都具有由[[鋁|鋁]]製成的前[[護木|護木]]，曾採用{{Link-en|KeyMod|KeyMod}}系統以添加附件，現已全數改用[[M-LOK|M-LOK]]。除槍機釋放按鈕外大部份操作部件都可左右手操作。MCX卡賓槍有四種類型的槍托可以選用。<ref name=GA/><ref name=warden/>

MCX採用了類似[[AR-18突擊步槍|AR-18]]緩衝彈簧，所以不像AR-15需要緩衝管，因此MCX的機匣尾部改為一段MIL-STD-1913導軌，提供更大的槍托安裝彈性。導軌槍托安裝介面亦被採用於如[[AR-18突擊步槍#BRN-180|BRN-180]]等無緩衝管的槍械。

另外因在AR系統上會出現磨損，因此在MCX上的槍栓導桿軌道、彈殼偏向器都為可替換鋼製部件，而槍機拉柄定位孔則加上鋼彈簧銷避免磨損上機匣。

SIG設計的上機匣可在裝上適配器以後與標準的[[AR-15半自動步槍|AR-15]]和[[M16突擊步槍|M16]]下機匣兼容。<ref name="GA"/><ref name="Merrill2015"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://soldiersystems.net/2015/02/09/ar-lower-receiver-extension-adapter-for-sig-mcx-upper/|title=AR Lower Receiver Extension Adapter for SIG MCX Upper - Soldier Systems Daily|access-date=2017-06-10|archive-date=2017-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170311013114/http://soldiersystems.net/2015/02/09/ar-lower-receiver-extension-adapter-for-sig-mcx-upper/|dead-url=no}}</ref>兩款步槍平台的整體佈局相似。<ref>{{cite web|quote=The MCX has the familiar AR upper and lower receiver layout that we know, but some caveats have been added here. The upper receiver is hardened in select areas, and Sig has developed replaceable parts for those areas that wear the most. One such part is the metal cam-path insert on the side of the upper receiver. Other replaceable parts include a feed ramp insert and the ambidextrous charging handle latch. These items are all steel inserts or pins. The forward assist has an aluminum housing that can be replaced if it wears out. These features reveal that the MCX was meant for long-term use in harsh conditions. In essence, you won’t have to scrap the upper receiver after hard use, only replace some parts. The lower receiver’s controls require no retraining, as they are the same as an AR’s, while the magazine release, bolt release and safety selector are all ambidextrous. Aftermarket drop-in triggers will be right at home, too.|url=http://www.tactical-life.com/firearms/review-sig-sauer-mcx/#mcx-twa15-lead|title=Sig Sauer’s MCX Rifle: An Elite Modular Weapons System|date=30 June 2015|first=Sean|last=Utley|publisher=Tactical Life|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2016-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161014031542/http://www.tactical-life.com/firearms/review-sig-sauer-mcx/#mcx-twa15-lead|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 衍生型 ==
=== MCX ===
*'''MCX卡賓槍'''：卡賓槍型，具有16英寸（410毫米）槍管。民用型採用半自動扳機組，軍警型則提供採用全自動扳機組。<ref name=GA/>
*'''MCX SBR'''：{{Link-en|短管步槍|Short-barreled rifle}}型，具有9英寸（230毫米）槍管。設有半自動民用型及全自動軍警型。根據美國聯邦法律，槍管短於16英寸（410毫米）的步槍都是歸類為{{Link-en|第二類槍械|Title II weapons}}，而這類武器受美國聯邦的限制，以及國家法律的監管。<ref name=GA/>
*'''MCX Pistol SBX'''：[[半自動手槍|半自動手槍]]型，具有9英寸（230毫米）槍管，[[SB_Tactical|手臂支撐器]]和半自動扳機組。這個版本符合美國法律定義的“手槍”，因為槍身設計成可與射手的身體單點接觸；<ref>Federal Gun Control Act 1968 [https://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/text/18/921 18 U.S. Code § 921 - Definitions] {{Wayback|url=https://www.law.cornell.edu/uscode/text/18/921 |date=20160102045939 }}, Cornell.edu, "(29) The term “handgun” means— (A) a firearm which has a short stock and is designed to be held and fired by the use of a single hand"</ref>雖然在一般來講，它是一種緊湊卡賓槍，因為它發射[[中间型威力枪弹|中間型威力]][[步枪|步枪]][[子彈|子彈]]。[[美國菸酒槍炮及爆裂物管理局|美國菸酒槍炮及爆裂物管理局]]曾警告使用者使用裝上了SIG SBX或類似的前臂支托的武器肩射，而且不是作為短管步槍註冊的話，仍視同短管步槍，也就是其中一款第二類槍械。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.grandviewoutdoors.com/grand-view-outdoors/the-rise-and-fall-of-the-sb-15-sig-brace/|title=The Rise And Fall Of The SB-15 ‘Sig Brace’|website=Grand View Outdoors|date=24 March 2015|access-date=2016-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161025092346/http://www.grandviewoutdoors.com/grand-view-outdoors/the-rise-and-fall-of-the-sb-15-sig-brace/|archive-date=2016-10-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
*'''MCX LVAW'''：低能見度突擊武器（{{Lang-en|Low Visibility Assault Weapon}}），為短管、[[抑制器|消聲]]、[[擊發調變槍械|擊發調變]]衍生型，只向執法機關和軍用市場提供。其綽號為“[[黑曼巴蛇|黑曼巴蛇]]”（Black Mamba）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.militarytimes.com/story/military/gearscout/2014/04/17/on-the-range-with-sig-sauers-mcx-black-mamba/32150065/|title=On the range with Sig Sauer's MCX 'Black Mamba'|website=Military Times|date=17 April 2014|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2016-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013092834/http://www.militarytimes.com/story/military/gearscout/2014/04/17/on-the-range-with-sig-sauers-mcx-black-mamba/32150065/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Neville2016">{{cite book|last=Neville|first=Leigh|title=Guns of Special Forces 2001 – 2015|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=v1yqCwAAQBAJ&pg=PA142|date=31 March 2016|publisher=Casemate Publishing|isbn=978-1-4738-8102-0|pages=142–143|access-date=2016-10-21|archive-date=2017-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170320234853/https://books.google.com/books?id=v1yqCwAAQBAJ&pg=PA142|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== MCX VIRTUS ===
2017年，西格&紹爾宣布的半自動型MCX系列步槍<ref name="test" />，並重新命名為MCX VIRTUS系列。MCX VIRTUS步槍裝有經重新設計而與之前的MCX版本互不兼容的上機匣、護木、槍管和[[槍栓|槍栓]]。此外，所有以前提及[[7.62×39mm|7.62×39毫米蘇聯口徑]]槍管套件的參考資料都已經從視覺上排除掉；口徑選項為[[5.56×45mm_NATO|5.56×45毫米]][[北大西洋公约组织|北约]]和{{Link-en|300 AAC Blackout (7.62×35mm)|300 AAC Blackout (7.62×35mm)|.300 AAC BLK（7.62×35毫米）}}口徑。原廠握把改為類似Magpul MOE的設計，SIG稱其為「小角度（Reduced Angle）握把」。

*'''MCX VIRTUS Patrol'''：標準型，SIG稱其為巡邏型。口徑為5.56NATO，16英寸（410毫米）槍管，1:7英寸[[膛線#缠率|膛線纏距]]，與定制西格Matchlite Duo扳機以提高精確度，折疊及5段位置伸縮式[[槍托|槍托]]，四款可供選擇的[[護木|護木]]長度，可互換的[[槍管|槍管]]和特殊的內部緩沖系統<ref name="SIg Sauer MCX Virtus">{{cite web|url=https://www.sigsauer.com/products/firearms/rifles/sig-mcx-virtus/|title=存档副本|accessdate=2018-03-18|archive-date=2018-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180306062541/https://www.sigsauer.com/products/firearms/rifles/sig-mcx-virtus/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="11.5">{{cite web|url=https://www.gunsamerica.com/digest/ready-mission-sig-sauer-mcx-virtus-full-review/|title=Ready for Any Mission: SIG Sauer MCX Virtus — Full Review|website=gunsamerica.com|language=en|access-date=January 5, 2019|first=Clay|last=Martin|archive-date=2019-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106060736/https://www.gunsamerica.com/digest/ready-mission-sig-sauer-mcx-virtus-full-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sigsauer.com/store/sig-mcx-virtus-patrol.html|title=Sig MCX VIRTUS Patrol|website=sigsauer.com|language=en|access-date=January 5, 2019|archive-date=2019-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106065329/https://www.sigsauer.com/store/sig-mcx-virtus-patrol.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*'''MCX VIRTUS SBR'''：短管步槍型，5.56 NATO口徑對應11.5英寸（292.1毫米）槍管，而.300 BLK口徑對應9英寸&5.5英寸（230毫米&140毫米）槍管<ref name="test" /><ref name="11.5true">{{cite web|url=https://www.sigsauer.com/store/sig-mcx-virtus-sbr.html|title=Sig MCX VIRTUS SBR|website=sigsauer.com|language=en|access-date=January 5, 2019|archive-date=2019-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106061439/https://www.sigsauer.com/store/sig-mcx-virtus-sbr.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*'''MCX VIRTUS PCB'''：VIRTUS SBR手槍版本，改用PCB手臂支撐器代替槍托，5.56 NATO口徑對應11.5英寸槍管，.300 BLK口徑對應9英寸槍管<ref name="test" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sigsauer.com/store/sig-mcx-virtus-pistol.html|title=Sig MCX VIRTUS Pistol|website=sigsauer.com|language=en|access-date=January 5, 2019|archive-date=2019-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106072303/https://www.sigsauer.com/store/sig-mcx-virtus-pistol.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== MCX Rattler ===
MCX Rattler（響尾蛇）為MCX[[個人防衛武器|個人防衛武器]]型。採用了較一般MCX為短的上機匣及較小的握把。另外復進助推器亦被移除。

* '''MCX Rattler SBR'''：短管步槍型。採用5.5英寸槍管。設有[[5.56×45mm_NATO|5.56 NATO]]及.300 BLK兩種口徑。
* '''MCX Rattler PCB'''：手槍型。改用PCB手臂支撐器。採用5.5英吋槍管，設有.300 BLK一種口徑。
* '''MCX Rattler Canebrake'''：手槍型。改用SD M-LOK護木並配上SRD762訓練抑制器。採用5.5英吋槍管，設有.300 BLK一種口徑。

=== 進一步衍生型 ===
*'''MCX-MR'''（中距離）：[[半自动步枪|半自動]][[狙击步枪|狙擊步槍]]（[[精確射手步槍|精確射手步槍]]），發射[[7.62×51mm_NATO|7.62×51毫米]][[北大西洋公约组织|北约]][[口徑|口徑]]步枪子彈。它具有由Bartlein槍管公司製造，採用416[[不鏽鋼|不鏽鋼]]、{{Link-en|開槽化|Fluting (firearms)}}的16英寸（410毫米）[[槍管|槍管]]，纏距為1:10。[[護木|護木]]通過一根插銷及一根螺銷固定，而導氣系統則具有裝上消聲器與不裝上消聲器時使用的兩個設定的氣體調節器。它的重量為8.9磅（4.0千克），並同時設有T型及左側槍機拉柄兩種配置，其中T型槍機拉柄改為翻轉180度以更換左右操作。可使用[[SR-25狙擊步槍|SR-25]]{{Link-en|規格彈匣|SR-25 pattern magazine}}，並與SR-25的下機匣兼容。[[西格&紹爾|西格&紹爾]]用以參與2012年美國陸軍緊湊型半自動狙擊系統（Compact Semi-Automatic Sniper System，CSASS）計劃的採用試驗，但得標的是[[黑克勒&科赫|黑克勒&科赫]]的[[HK_G28狙擊步槍|G28E狙擊步槍]]。<ref name="Merrill-MR">{{cite web|url=http://www.recoilweb.com/recoil-exclusive-sig-sauer-csass-the-mcx-mr-65405.html|first=David|last=Merrill|publisher=Recoil|title=RECOIL Exclusive: An Inside Look at Sig Sauer’s CSASS – The MCX-MR|date=21 May 2015|accessdate=2016-10-21|archive-date=2016-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160922045335/http://www.recoilweb.com/recoil-exclusive-sig-sauer-csass-the-mcx-mr-65405.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Jahner|first=Kyle|title=H&K confirms: This is the Army's new and improved sniper rifle|url=http://www.armytimes.com/story/military/2016/04/08/hk-confirms-armys-new-and-improved-sniper-rifle/82788202/|access-date=9 June 2016|website=Army Times|date=8 April 2016}}</ref>
*'''MCX SPEAR'''：SIG Sauer用於參加次世代班用步槍（{{Lang-en|Next Generation Squad Weapons - Rifle}}，簡稱NGSW-R）的衍生型。採用.227 FURY（6.8×51毫米）SIG Hybrid鋼銅混合彈殼彈藥及採用SR-25規格彈匣。加入雙邊槍機釋放鈕，而可翻轉T型槍機拉柄改為一般MCX的雙邊槍機拉柄。可更換槍管使用[[7.62×51mm_NATO|7.62×51毫米]][[北大西洋公约组织|北约]][[口徑|口徑]]步枪子彈，並且設有兩段（NORMAL-ADVERSE）可調導氣座<ref>{{Cite web|title=[TFB GUNFEST] The SIG Sauer MCX Spear NGSW Rifle -|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2021/01/15/tfb-gunfest-the-sig-sauer-mcx-spear-ngsw-rifle/|accessdate=2021-01-15|date=2021-01-15|work=The Firearm Blog|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220123094327/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2021/01/15/tfb-gunfest-the-sig-sauer-mcx-spear-ngsw-rifle/}}</ref>，SIG Sauer在NGSW系統中採用供電導軌以安裝配件。在2019年國際防務裝備展（DSEI）中展出為13英寸槍管型，並裝上MIL-SLX68-QD抑制器<ref>{{Cite web|title=TFB First Look: SIG Sauer's Next Generation Squad Weapons -|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2019/09/12/tfb-first-look-sig-sauers-next-generation-squad-weapons/|accessdate=2020-05-17|date=2019-09-12|work=The Firearm Blog|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191206081708/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2019/09/12/tfb-first-look-sig-sauers-next-generation-squad-weapons/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=L3Harris Technologies - Vortex Optics to develop fire control system for 6.8mm Next Generation Squad Weapon|url=https://www.armyrecognition.com/april_2020_news_defense_global_security_army_industry/l3harris_technologies_-_vortex_optics_to_develop_fire_control_system_for_6.8mm_next_generation_squad_weapon.html|accessdate=2020-05-17|author=|date=|format=|work=www.armyrecognition.com|publisher=|language=|archive-date=2020-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427180237/https://www.armyrecognition.com/april_2020_news_defense_global_security_army_industry/l3harris_technologies_-_vortex_optics_to_develop_fire_control_system_for_6.8mm_next_generation_squad_weapon.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年，在一次訪問中SIG的[[行銷長|CMO]] Tom Taylor表示在兩年內一定會推出MCX SPEAR的民用版本，唯價格絕不便宜<ref>{{Cite web|title=Big News, a Little Reminiscing, and the 10mm: A Candid Interview with SIG Sauer -|url=https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2020/08/12/big-news-a-little-reminiscing-and-the-10mm-a-candid-interview-with-sig-sauer/|accessdate=2020-08-13|date=2020-08-12|work=The Firearm Blog|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422203453/https://www.thefirearmblog.com/blog/2020/08/12/big-news-a-little-reminiscing-and-the-10mm-a-candid-interview-with-sig-sauer/}}</ref>。於2022年4月成為NGSW計畫得標者。名為XM5預計將替換M4/M4A1步槍。

